      <proof>
        <p>
          Since the construction of <m>A\left\langle \tfrac{f_1}{g},\dots,\tfrac{f_n}{g} \right\rangle</m>
          factors through <m>A[1/g]</m>, we first note that <m>A \to A[1/g]</m> is flat
          (either by <xref ref="lem-flat-mult-f"/> or simply by writing 
          <m>A^{\triangleright}[1/g] = \colim (A^{\triangleright} \stackrel{\times g}{\to} A^{\triangleright} \stackrel{\times g}{\to} \cdots)</m>).
