        <p>
          We then note that <m>A\left\langle f_1,\dots,f_n\right\rangle</m> can be factored as a sequence of rational localizations with parameters <m>f_i,1</m>
          for <m>i=1,\dots,n</m>. We thus reduce to the case <m>n = 1</m>.
