    <theorem xml:id="thm-localization-is-flat-liquid">
      <statement>
        <p>
          For <m>A</m> an analytic ring and <m>q \in A^{\gas}</m> a unit,
          choose <m>f_1,\dots,f_n,g \in A^{\triangleright}(*)</m>
          (not necessarily generating the unit ideal). 
          Then
          <m>A\to A\left\langle \tfrac{f_1}{g},\dots,\tfrac{f_n}{g} \right\rangle^\dagger_q</m>
